[Reference
----------
van Dorp L, Richard D, Tan CCS, et al. No evidence for increased transmissibility from recurrent mutations in SARS-CoV-2. Nat Commun 11, 5986 (2020). https://doi.org/10.1038/s41467-020-19818-2]

